title: Ritahavesolution
tags:
---
Amo: Rita, I think... I think I know why you came to the store!
<<set $tempBool = false>>
<<nodeStatus StarRingDialogueSystem repair_service $tempBool>>
<<set $tempBool1 = false>>
<<nodeStatus StarRingDialogueSystem magic_research $tempBool1>>
<<set $tempBool2 = false>>
<<nodeStatus StarRingDialogueSystem refund_soda $tempBool2>>
<<set $tempBool3 = false>>
